---
import BaseHead from '../components/BaseHead.astro';
import { SITE_DESCRIPTION, SITE_TITLE } from '../consts';
---

<!doctype html>
<html lang="zh-CN">
	<head>
		<BaseHead title={SITE_TITLE} description={SITE_DESCRIPTION} />
	</head>
	<body>
		<div class="container">
			<div class="profile">
				<img src="https://ww-aibot-img-1258476243.cos.ap-guangzhou.myqcloud.com/J5Jgnzc/7616336549981772661?sign=q-sign-algorithm%3Dsha1%26q-ak%3DAKIDbBpaJvdLBvpnibcYcfyPuaO5f9U1UoGo%26q-sign-time%3D1773316541%3B1773316841%26q-key-time%3D1773316541%3B1773316841%26q-header-list%3D%26q-url-param-list%3D%26q-signature%3D74348e9d6ef0d1cfa461c889a7a298082faa00fa" alt="XuWeiJie" />
				<div>
					<h1>XuWeiJie</h1>
					<p class="position">量子计算研究者</p>
					<p class="contact">
						📧 <a href="mailto:your-email@example.com">Email</a> · 
						🐙 <a href="https://github.com/utopiapp123">GitHub</a> · 
						📍 中国
					</p>
				</div>
			</div>
			
			<section>
				<h2>Research</h2>
				<p>我专注于量子计算领域的前沿研究，主要研究方向包括：</p>
				<ul class="research-interests">
					<li>变分量子算法（VQE/VQA）</li>
					<li>量子联邦学习</li>
					<li>量子分布式计算</li>
					<li>量子机器学习</li>
				</ul>
			</section>
			
			<section>
				<h2>Publications</h2>
				<div class="publication">
					<p class="pub-title">Quantum Distributed Computing: Algorithms and Protocols</p>
					<p class="pub-authors"><strong>XuWeiJie</strong></p>
					<p class="pub-venue">GitHub, 2026</p>
					<p class="pub-links"><a href="https://github.com/utopiapp123/quantum-distributed" target="_blank" rel="noopener">[Code]</a></p>
				</div>
				<div class="publication">
					<p class="pub-title">Quantum Federated Learning: Privacy-Preserving Quantum Machine Learning</p>
					<p class="pub-authors"><strong>XuWeiJie</strong></p>
					<p class="pub-venue">GitHub, 2026</p>
					<p class="pub-links"><a href="https://github.com/utopiapp123/quantum-federated-learning" target="_blank" rel="noopener">[Code]</a></p>
				</div>
			</section>
			
			<section>
				<h2>Experience</h2>
				<div class="experience-item">
					<p class="exp-title">量子计算研究</p>
					<p class="exp-meta">2024 - 至今</p>
					<p class="exp-desc">专注于变分量子算法、量子联邦学习等方向的研究</p>
				</div>
				<div class="experience-item">
					<p class="exp-title">全栈开发者</p>
					<p class="exp-meta">2020 - 至今</p>
					<p class="exp-desc">Python、TypeScript、量子计算框架</p>
				</div>
			</section>
			
			<footer>
				<p>&copy; 2026 XuWeiJie. Built with Astro.</p>
			</footer>
		</div>
	</body>
</html>

<style>
	* {
		box-sizing: border-box;
	}
	
	body {
		font-family: 'Georgia', 'Times New Roman', serif;
		background: #fafafa;
		color: #333;
		line-height: 1.6;
		margin: 0;
		padding: 0;
	}
	
	.container {
		max-width: 800px;
		margin: 0 auto;
		padding: 3em 1.5em;
	}
	
	.profile {
		display: flex;
		gap: 2em;
		align-items: flex-start;
		padding-bottom: 2em;
		margin-bottom: 2.5em;
		border-bottom: 2px solid #ddd;
	}
	
	.profile img {
		width: 160px;
		height: 160px;
		border-radius: 4px;
		object-fit: cover;
		border: 1px solid #ddd;
		flex-shrink: 0;
	}
	
	.profile h1 {
		font-size: 2em;
		margin: 0 0 0.3em 0;
		color: #222;
		font-weight: normal;
	}
	
	.position {
		font-size: 1.1em;
		color: #666;
		margin: 0 0 0.8em 0;
	}
	
	.contact {
		font-size: 0.95em;
		color: #555;
		margin: 0;
	}
	
	.contact a {
		color: #0d9488;
		text-decoration: none;
	}
	
	.contact a:hover {
		text-decoration: underline;
	}
	
	section {
		margin-bottom: 2.5em;
	}
	
	h2 {
		font-size: 1.5em;
		margin: 0 0 1em 0;
		color: #222;
		font-weight: normal;
		border-bottom: 1px solid #eee;
		padding-bottom: 0.5em;
	}
	
	p {
		margin: 0 0 1em 0;
	}
	
	.research-interests {
		padding-left: 1.5em;
	}
	
	.research-interests li {
		margin-bottom: 0.5em;
	}
	
	.publication {
		margin-bottom: 1.5em;
		padding-left: 1em;
		border-left: 3px solid #0d9488;
	}
	
	.pub-title {
		font-weight: bold;
		color: #222;
		margin-bottom: 0.3em;
	}
	
	.pub-authors {
		font-size: 0.95em;
		color: #555;
		margin-bottom: 0.3em;
	}
	
	.pub-venue {
		font-size: 0.9em;
		color: #777;
		font-style: italic;
		margin-bottom: 0.5em;
	}
	
	.pub-links a {
		color: #0d9488;
		text-decoration: none;
		margin-right: 1em;
		font-size: 0.9em;
	}
	
	.experience-item {
		margin-bottom: 1.5em;
	}
	
	.exp-title {
		font-weight: bold;
		color: #222;
		margin-bottom: 0.2em;
	}
	
	.exp-meta {
		font-size: 0.9em;
		color: #777;
		margin-bottom: 0.5em;
	}
	
	.exp-desc {
		color: #555;
		margin: 0;
	}
	
	footer {
		text-align: center;
		padding-top: 2em;
		margin-top: 3em;
		border-top: 1px solid #ddd;
		color: #999;
		font-size: 0.85em;
	}
	
	a {
		color: #0d9488;
	}
	
	@media (max-width: 600px) {
		.profile {
			flex-direction: column;
			align-items: center;
			text-align: center;
		}
		
		.profile img {
			width: 140px;
			height: 140px;
		}
		
		.contact {
			text-align: left;
		}
		
		.container {
			padding: 2em 1em;
		}
	}
</style>
